{"tid":93414,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"跟住佛you 砌水仙","createTime":"2017-01-24T11:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T02:14:58.000Z","uid":71467,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d29ee1205713ade70a41df3e55d42ff0c49712","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今年得閒無事做<br />\n走左去年宵花市打工打兩日<br />\n邊到就唔講啦<br />\n目的都唔係想宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為好多人都會買水仙頭翻去<br />\n但又唔識砌喎<br />\n其實就好撚柒易<br />\n係咁易同大家講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5ffd5fdcfcc9bdf2aa8b1656f6730a7a8c16c0","tid":93414,"uid":16885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:51:55.000Z","msg":"年宵工點搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4cef3e824444076c16a8b8a589cf8a3cb528d0","tid":93414,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:52:57.000Z","msg":"我剩係記得細個啲人話水仙有毒"},{"pid":"12a0504b3e3f16d964827ec3c7e9cbbe1176e27b","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:53:29.000Z","msg":"首先一定要帶手套啦<br />\n因為水仙係強鹼黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔咁用手處理隻手會變到好乾燥乏味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後就選翻個靚水仙<br />\n點先叫靚呢<br />\n就唔化睇佢大唔大舊既<br />\n買大舊定細舊主要係睇翻你個盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係要睇佢生得平唔平均<br />\n最重要有幾多花蕾<br />\n正常水仙有6個以上<br />\n而手上依個係可遇不可求既8昌<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/194921_4cb37810e090d1bb5971efcc0dd71bf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F194921_4cb37810e090d1bb5971efcc0dd71bf1.jpg&h=1a331029&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d02bc60bffc8de644f85ee7a1f060659dc3247b","tid":93414,"uid":36262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"e0143a01ffa93a22883a04a3ffb11a42b725859c","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尋日有個啊叔叫我啊姐<br />\n叫我幫佢搵d 8、9昌既水仙俾佢<br />\n我立即屌佢老母啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v2FL768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv2FL768.jpg&h=a216e5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留你老母食狗屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 唔懮做"},{"pid":"d92bb25aa5d3decb2f204f7d22752b81fdb028c1","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:00:45.000Z","msg":"因為運貨過黎要省位<br />\n所以呢通常水仙d根都痴尻住曬<br />\n藕斷絲連既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v92Ry8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v92Ry8.jpg&h=2e95a823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你格硬分開佢地<br />\n係會立即比店員(即係我)<br />\n屌老母既<br />\n因為一整親d根就好易死、唔靚<br />\n有命你叫叫命根子嘛對不對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b1696ffa928f59f633fc21b492c26d8bcb3926","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年宵工點搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識人<br />\n多數請朋友、親戚多<br />\n最多fd搭fd<br />\n基本唔會公開請"},{"pid":"991a4d5e18c5e199a4947c0eee40a3ad226e8ecc","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我剩係記得細個啲人話水仙有毒</blockquote><br />\n當然<br />\n不過正常見到咁多根都唔會想放入口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972d8e7ebb537f3bc383b23da642903ca0e5c619","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lm</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0e62ba4c36d2c3e5041367430d71c461c81849","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"咁應該點分開佢地呢？<br />\n<br />\n正確做法係揸住佢地<br />\n上上下下左左右右咁扭下蚊下<br />\n佢地就會分開嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/200738_e2418f874c9005d6dae95803dce0753d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F200738_e2418f874c9005d6dae95803dce0753d.jpg&h=fd9669e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/200739_68b6d7dcfd7b27ae4a63bed9f03e3120.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F200739_68b6d7dcfd7b27ae4a63bed9f03e3120.jpg&h=7151a4fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然係要兩隻手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93de93198259572be7f90e110a2077fef0a737d1","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:09:23.000Z","msg":"推下post"},{"pid":"a5c3388a54ae33f2f41ba9135db7019d1cfeb623","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99872d97095721f41d8cddbf5d1ac72fd6505bb7","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:18:38.000Z","msg":"成功分開左佢地之後<br />\n你會發現水仙身上有好多啡色既皮<br />\n就咁met左佢就得啦<br />\n<br />\n其實d皮就好似洋蔥咁<br />\nmet完會生翻出黎<br />\n外面個層都係會愈養愈啡的<br />\n所以你懶唔met都無問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/201622_b528717cd26dc232271b2747198bcf2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F201622_b528717cd26dc232271b2747198bcf2b.jpg&h=6cb94f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nmet完就靚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/201836_a96cbc634421b663f34439388370f5d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F201836_a96cbc634421b663f34439388370f5d2.jpg&h=0db46417&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eac86a1d20cad56020d1ee248f4da8c7d84e1da8","tid":93414,"uid":52051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1bb6ad2f73b97513365be1250f38a15f388cb5","tid":93414,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"你一來貨就浸好晒，你有冇開過箱？<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/203016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F203016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=636c38be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我每年要界70盒，每盒十個<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/202848_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F202848_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=649ed55b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c067ab68e57257a6841c70167c4248a7d6fed512","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:54:58.000Z","msg":"met完d皮之後<br />\n仲有d 無花蕾既草<br />\n如果想d花生得靚d<br />\n通常都會met左佢<br />\n但met唔met曬佢就自己睇心情啦<br />\n<br />\n然最隨便搵多個水仙<br />\n高定低都無所謂<br />\n一樣高咪話平頭<br />\n一路順風囉<br />\n有高有低咪話有d層次感咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡單d咁講<br />\n大家都係亂塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但通常單頭賣既會靚過入左盤既<br />\n因為入盤可以遮下d瑕疵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n砌完加條絲帶就搞撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1B6Kg0m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1B6Kg0m.jpg&h=e62f5204&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf824d7c6ddaf4e8d3d41de6d4898f7a6425fd0f","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"同埋其實d水仙生定熟都無乜所謂<br />\n反正其實都一定過到年咁濟<br />\n係得d啊婆麻撚煩好執著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7eba6f9fd08a7c859635676f86ca298ab24250","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:56:42.000Z","msg":"砌左一個上就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好快又賣q曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/205620_41213c7eb8d34840aec73cb9c64e0b8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F205620_41213c7eb8d34840aec73cb9c64e0b8b.jpg&h=6c351f24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27def684857bd2b84697b281f4a8823ccc72828d","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2978845c79c9084f18816965dee4a83ba7ee235","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你一來貨就浸好晒，你有冇開過箱？<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/203016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F203016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=636c38be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我每年要界70盒，每盒十個<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/202848_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F202848_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=649ed55b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前要<br />\n不過好麻煩<br />\n買d浸好曬好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfd4860dee96066d8a1476550c440f630044281","tid":93414,"uid":64956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>砌左一個上就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好快又賣q曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/205620_41213c7eb8d34840aec73cb9c64e0b8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F205620_41213c7eb8d34840aec73cb9c64e0b8b.jpg&h=6c351f24&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n黃色幾錢一盤?自己砌又慳幾多?"},{"pid":"0ecbf731948f616cf535edee4ead7f8682da7726","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:16:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>砌左一個上就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好快又賣q曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/205620_41213c7eb8d34840aec73cb9c64e0b8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F205620_41213c7eb8d34840aec73cb9c64e0b8b.jpg&h=6c351f24&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n黃色幾錢一盤?自己砌又慳幾多?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n188好似<br />\n省少少囉<br />\n40蚊個水仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38645ea804bf6d9778a4e403a19766d13d5a6d96","tid":93414,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:17:52.000Z","msg":"講真唔好年年都買新盤<br />\n唔想或者唔識自己砌的話<br />\n就拎落去年宵市場比d人砌啦<br />\n搵d有賣單頭個d<br />\n唔好咁浪費嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2d1b1a0bf6ae26bf7ae60462245ad39128ca03","tid":93414,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"留名學野~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}